, \u201cThe garment of a Muslim should be lowered to the middle of the shin, but there is no harm or blame in what is between it and the ankles. Whatever is lower than the ankles\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15189,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/21\/salat-trail-pride-not-accepted\/","url_meta":{"origin":43170,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Vanity: Prayer not accepted in trailing garments","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 21, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: While a man was praying with his garment draped below himself, the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cGo and perform ablution.\u201d The man went and performed ablution, then he came to the Prophet. The Prophet said, \u201cGo and perform ablution.\u201d The man\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25643,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/12\/19\/dignified-pleasant-hygiene\/","url_meta":{"origin":43170,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Cleanliness: Display a dignified, pleasant appearance","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 19, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn Abdullah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, came to us and he saw an unkempt man with disheveled hair. The Prophet said, \u201cCould this man find nothing to groom his hair?\u201d The Prophet saw another man with a dirty garment and he said,\u2026","rel":"","context":